<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  
  <body>
       <center><h4> Your on duty request has been approved </h4></center> 

   <p>Your on duty request has been approved by <b><% emp=Employee.where(id: @employee.manager_id).take %><%= emp.try(:first_name) %> <%= emp.try(:middle_name) %> <%= emp.try(:last_name) %> from date <b> <%= @od_request.start_date.to_date %></b> to<b> <%= @od_request.end_date.to_date%></b></p>


 

<h4>Details of the on duty :-</h4>

 

<p>Total Number of days :- <%= @od_request.leave_count %></p>

 

<p>Reason :- <%= @od_request.reason %></p>

 

<h4>Requester Details :- <h4>

 

<p>Employee ID :- <%= @od_request.employee.try(:manual_employee_code) %></p>

 

<p>Employee Name :- <%= @od_request.employee.try(:first_name) %> <%= @od_request.employee.try(:middle_name) %> <%= @od_request.employee.try(:last_name) %></p>
  </body>
</html>

